ygData.msgSnippet: Dictate is nearly unresistable, however if he is lvl 60 no dice, too high. ... From: alexander.jones@foreningssparbanken.se
ygData.messageBody:
Dictate is nearly unresistable, however if he is lvl 60 no dice, too high.

-----Original Message-----
From: alexander.jones@...
[mailto:alexander.jones@...]
Sent: Monday, May 21, 2001 4:01 AM
To: EverQuest@yahoogroups.com
Subject: RE: [EverQuest] Fire pot ports...


I cant recall the name. Its a grandmaster (monk class defined) and hes
around level60 with VERY HIGH mr. I believe hes quest related, and i doubt
very much you can get anything to stick on him.

/Alex

Interesting. Do you know the name of the Iksar NPC? How long does it take
him to kill Feydedar? Just wait till its near dead 45 seconds from dead
have a 60 enchanter Dictate the Iksar and loot up. But the Iksar is prob
too high to do that with.


Mu

path sooner or later.
